==English==
===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-both}}

#(''mainly UK; countable'') A plant (''Brassica napus''), a kind of [[turnip]], grown for the [[edible]] underground part of its [[stem]] (often considered to be, but not in fact, its root).
#(''mainly UK; uncountable'') The fleshy part of stem of the swede, eaten as a [[vegetable]].

====Synonyms====
*(''plant''): [[rutabaga]] (''US, Canada'') 
*(''vegetable''): [[rutabaga]] (''US, Canada'')

